<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Thank you for your purchase - Hygiene Pad Dispenser">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0A0F2D">
  <title>Pad Successfully Dispensed</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --razorpay-blue: #0B5FFF;
      --razorpay-dark: #0A0F2D;
      --razorpay-light: #F8F9FF;
      --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0F2D 0%, #1A1F3D 100%);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg-gradient);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      color: var(--razorpay-light);
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 440px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(11, 95, 255, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .success-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #00FF88;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: inline-block;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

    h1 {
      color: var(--razorpay-light);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #A0A7C7;
    }

    .status-card {
      background: rgba(11, 95, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .status-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .quote-card {
      background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #00FF88;
    }

    .quote {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #C0C7E7;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .author {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-align: right;
      color: #00FF88;
    }

    .back-button {
      background: transparent;
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--razorpay-blue);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--razorpay-blue);
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .back-button:hover {
      background: rgba(11, 95, 255, 0.1);
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
      100% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .container {
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
      
      .status-card {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      
      .quote-card {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
      
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <i class="fas fa-check-circle success-icon"></i>
      <h1>Thank You for Your Purchase</h1>
      <p>Your pad has been successfully dispensed.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="status-card">
      <div class="status-item">
        <span>Available Pads</span>
        <strong><%= padCount %></strong>
      </div>
      <div class="status-item">
        <span>Dispensing Status</span>
        <span style="color: #00FF88"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Complete</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>Please collect your pad from the dispensing tray below.</p>

    <div class="quote-card">
      <p class="quote">"A woman with a voice is, by definition, a strong woman. But the search to find that voice can be remarkably difficult."</p>
      <p class="author">â€” Melinda Gates</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="back-button">Return to Home</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Auto-redirect after 30 seconds
    setTimeout(function() {
      window.location.href = '/';
    }, 30000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>